        <abstract> 
<p><hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> has "stirred up the mud with a vengeance"; AG and three or four others have saved CD from annihilation and are responsible for the attention now given to the subject. Reports events at Oxford BAAS meeting.</p> 
            <p>New evidence supports AG’s view of a warm post-glacial period.</p>
            <p>Discusses his recent orchid observations.</p>
            <p>Poses AG a question on design in nature.</p>
        </abstract>
